Comment: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,距今100年前
Comment: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,出現了人類的天敵
Comment: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們與人類之間存在著壓倒性的力量差距
Comment: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類差點陷入滅絕的危機
Comment: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,存活下來的人類們建造了
Comment: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,瑪利亞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,席納之牆 三面城牆
Comment: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從此實現了100年的和平生活
Comment: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,845年
Comment: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因突然現身的超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以及盔甲巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,和平的日常與城牆一同被破壞
Comment: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類放棄了瑪利亞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失去了兩成的人口以及三分之一的領土
Comment: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,活動領域退至羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:01:09.91,0:01:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,850年
Comment: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因再次現身的超大型巨人 城牆再次被破壞
Comment: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又再次允許了巨人的進攻
Comment: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,兩小時後
Comment: 0,0:01:33.27,0:01:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所有的居民都完成了避難
Comment: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有居民被巨人吃掉
Comment: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,多虧士兵的迎擊任務之下
Comment: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果不算上犧牲的士兵的話...
Comment: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要有你在
Comment: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就無所不能
Comment: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請等等 隊長
Comment: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果巨人攻進來的話
Comment: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要我們這些補給兵來守住這裡是不可能的
Comment: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,拜託 您請留下來
Comment: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我滾開
Comment: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我接下來一定要去整頓增援部隊
Comment: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是在安全的後門之內是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你這傢伙想說什麼?
Comment: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是依照規定的行動
Comment: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,遵從規定執行任務 這才是士兵的職責
Comment: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果這裡被攻陷的話...
Comment: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我閉嘴!
Comment: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳再說下去 就視為抗命
Comment: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就不得不在這裡給妳制裁
Comment: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該已經聽見暫時撤退的鐘聲了
Comment: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼大家都不爬上城牆?
Comment: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經...
Comment: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不行了...
Comment: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都結束了...
Comment: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好了
Comment: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那種東西是有什麼用
Comment: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 約翰你說該怎麼辦啊
Comment: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還可以怎麼辦
Comment: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好不容易才發出了撤退命令
Comment: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但卻因為沒瓦斯而爬不上城牆
Comment: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我看我們所有人都會死在這
Comment: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都是那些廢物害的
Comment: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是補給班的那些人嗎?
Comment: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道全滅了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說是喪失了戰鬥意志
Comment: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然我能了解他們的心情
Comment: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼說也不可以放棄對我們的補給任務
Comment: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,躲在本部都不出來吧
Comment: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那棟樓被巨人圍困 無法進行瓦斯補給
Comment: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣的話
Comment: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們應該賭一把
Comment: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,設法幹掉那些巨人才對吧?
Comment: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們在這裡空等也是一樣的
Comment: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這邊巨人也會開始聚集起來
Comment: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,四處逃竄也只會把我們僅剩的瓦斯用光
Comment: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一旦失去了機動能力
Comment: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就真的不用玩了!
Comment: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你難得動腦了呢 柯尼
Comment: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是你覺得就以現在這裡的兵力辦得到嗎?
Comment: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前鋒的學長姐們幾乎是全滅
Comment: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們這些訓練兵裡又有誰能指揮這場殊死戰
Comment: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算有人指揮我們也無法對付那些巨人
Comment: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,恐怕瓦斯補給室裡有著很多三四公尺級的巨人吧
Comment: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當然在那種情況下是不可能執行作業的
Comment: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒辦法了嗎...
Comment: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是無聊的人生
Comment: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣的話 還不如早點跟她說...
Comment: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再拚一下啦 各位
Comment: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來 站起來
Comment: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要大家同心協力
Comment: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定能夠成功的
Comment: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會帶領大家的
Comment: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,和大家一起...
Comment: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,萊納 你打算怎樣?
Comment: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,時機還沒到
Comment: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要打 就等大家到齊了再說
Comment: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不行吧... 不管怎麼想...
Comment: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們都無法離開這城市而且還會全滅...
Comment: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並不是說沒有做好陣亡的覺悟
Comment: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們究竟為了什麼而死?
Comment: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳不是後衛嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮
Comment: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我大概了解整個情況了
Comment: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過
Comment: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對於我帶有私人感情的問題要先向妳道歉
Comment: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳有沒有看到艾連他們那班?
Comment: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒看到
Comment: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或許爬上城牆的班有看到
Comment: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對了 阿爾敏在那邊
Comment: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不行
Comment: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我到底有什麼臉見她
Comment: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只是苟且偷生罷了
Comment: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,早知如此
Comment: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個時候乾脆一起死了算了
Comment: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒受傷吧
Comment: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事吧
Comment: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連在哪裡?
Comment: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們...
Comment: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,訓練兵34班...
Comment: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,托瑪斯．瓦格納
