Comment: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明直接跑來攻擊我們還比較正常...
Comment: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我感覺他有著格鬥技的概念
Comment: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那到底...
Comment: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也只能說他是奇行種吧
Comment: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不清楚的地方還有很多
Comment: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總之我們趕快前往本部吧
Comment: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等等 米卡莎的瓦斯罐是空的
Comment: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,屁啦 真的嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼辦啊 沒有妳的話
Comment: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能做的很明顯
Comment: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然我的也所剩不多
Comment: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,趕快跟我的交換
Comment: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏...
Comment: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,除此之外別無他法了
Comment: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算給我也沒有意義
Comment: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次請妳好好珍惜的使用
Comment: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是為了拯救大家
Comment: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒有做好「背負著大家的生命」的覺悟就煽動戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在沒有感受到這份責任之前
Comment: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,甚至還曾經放棄過自己的生命
Comment: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且還只是為了自己
Comment: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好了!
Comment: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,機動裝置還可以用
Comment: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,刀子也補滿了
Comment: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只是...
Comment: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個東西請留下來給我
Comment: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我果然...
Comment: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是不想要活著被吃掉
Comment: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不...不會吧...
Comment: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不會把你丟在這裡的
Comment: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個時候
Comment: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他只是不斷地攻擊
Comment: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人把巨人殺死這種事...
Comment: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我聽都沒聽過
Comment: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然而我感到些許興奮
Comment: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那片光景
Comment: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看起來就像是人類憤怒的表現
Comment: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,殘殺巨人的巨人
Comment: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因其出現在眼前而動彈不得
Comment: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,瞠目結舌的第104期訓練兵們
Comment: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最終 在他們面前現身的是...
