Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}距今100年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出現了人類的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們與人類之間存在著壓倒性的力量差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類差點陷入滅絕的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}存活下來的人類們建造了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}瑪利亞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}席納之牆 三面城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從此實現了100年的和平生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}845年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因突然現身的超大型巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及盔甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}和平的日常與城牆一同被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類放棄了瑪利亞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}失去了兩成的人口以及三分之一的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}活動領域退至羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.91,0:01:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}850年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因再次現身的超大型巨人 城牆再次被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又再次允許了巨人的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}兩小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.27,0:01:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所有的居民都完成了避難
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有居民被巨人吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}多虧士兵的迎擊任務之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果不算上犧牲的士兵的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就無所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請等等 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果巨人攻進來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要我們這些補給兵來守住這裡是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}拜託 您請留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我接下來一定要去整頓增援部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是在安全的後門之內是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這傢伙想說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是依照規定的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}遵從規定執行任務 這才是士兵的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果這裡被攻陷的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳再說下去 就視為抗命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就不得不在這裡給妳制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該已經聽見暫時撤退的鐘聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼大家都不爬上城牆?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不行了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都結束了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那種東西是有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 約翰你說該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還可以怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好不容易才發出了撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但卻因為沒瓦斯而爬不上城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我看我們所有人都會死在這
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都是那些廢物害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是補給班的那些人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道全滅了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說是喪失了戰鬥意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然我能了解他們的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼說也不可以放棄對我們的補給任務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}躲在本部都不出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那棟樓被巨人圍困 無法進行瓦斯補給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們應該賭一把
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}設法幹掉那些巨人才對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們在這裡空等也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這邊巨人也會開始聚集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}四處逃竄也只會把我們僅剩的瓦斯用光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一旦失去了機動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就真的不用玩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你難得動腦了呢 柯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是你覺得就以現在這裡的兵力辦得到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前鋒的學長姐們幾乎是全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們這些訓練兵裡又有誰能指揮這場殊死戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算有人指揮我們也無法對付那些巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}恐怕瓦斯補給室裡有著很多三四公尺級的巨人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}當然在那種情況下是不可能執行作業的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒辦法了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是無聊的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣的話 還不如早點跟她說...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再拚一下啦 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要大家同心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一定能夠成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會帶領大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}和大家一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}萊納 你打算怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}時機還沒到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要打 就等大家到齊了再說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不行吧... 不管怎麼想...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們都無法離開這城市而且還會全滅...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並不是說沒有做好陣亡的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們究竟為了什麼而死?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳不是後衛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我大概了解整個情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對於我帶有私人感情的問題要先向妳道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳有沒有看到艾連他們那班?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}或許爬上城牆的班有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對了 阿爾敏在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我到底有什麼臉見她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我只是苟且偷生罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}早知如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個時候乾脆一起死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}訓練兵34班...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}托瑪斯．瓦格納
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奈克．提亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米力伍斯．賽姆斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米娜．卡羅萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連．葉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以上五位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都完成了自己的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}最後壯烈地犧牲了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}34班幾乎全滅啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果我們直接去和巨人對幹也會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起 米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連他...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了救我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我卻什麼都做不到...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在不是感傷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果幹掉了在本部的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就能夠補充瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家就能爬上城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯... 是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是就算有妳在...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那種數量...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我很強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}比你們還要強 非常的強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我能夠把那邊的巨人們全部幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算只有我一人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而你們全都是沒用的俗辣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}膽小又窩囊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}非常令人遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們只要在這裡吸手指就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吸著之後給我看著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等 米卡莎妳突然說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道妳想一人對抗那種數量的巨人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種事情怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不戰鬥就只有死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}贏了的話就能活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但不去戰鬥又怎麼會贏?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}令人感到遺憾的是妳的表達能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}竟然想用那種話來激我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都是你害的 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們有學過要眼睜睜地看著夥伴獨自戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們這樣可真的會變成俗辣喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這傢伙還真是意料之外
