Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.65,SP-EG,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You can't hide your self You can't run
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:24.22,SP-EG,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}We're fighting for our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.85,SP-EG,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}And we just can not lose again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.58,SP-EG,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}There's not much time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.79,SP-EG,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2} Be ready to fight  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:32.89,SP-EG,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Do it!
