Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.65,SPG-CH,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你無處可躲 無處可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:24.22,SPG-CH,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我們在為生存而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.85,SPG-CH,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}而且我們非贏不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.58,SPG-CH,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}時間緊迫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.79,SPG-CH,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}準備戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:32.89,SPG-CH,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}上吧!
