Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那些傢伙... 混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要打就打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟著米卡莎走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總而言之速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在瓦斯耗盡之前殺入本部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過 米卡莎還真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是要怎樣才能夠像她那麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不 她噴射瓦斯用太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣的話立刻就會耗盡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算技術再好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒了機動能力我們也就毫無用處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她果然 沒有像平常一樣的冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是用行動試圖掩蓋動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣下去...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}遲早會...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰! 你去引導大家戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我去追阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:45.73,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹嘛? 巨人可還在那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在大家需要你的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我又失去了家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再次...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我想起這種痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又要從這裡再重新開始嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}連靠近本部都沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不抱持著會犧牲的覺悟的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}糟糕 那傢伙瓦斯耗盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別過來!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}湯姆 我馬上去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別去!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我為什麼沒能阻止他...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼沒有阻止到...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果強硬地去阻止他的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就不會這樣了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我有這資格嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}站在「負起責任」這個立場的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要... 我不想死...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個世界真是殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然而...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}卻如此的美好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是個美好的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我明明已經放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為何...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我又站了起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為何...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要垂死掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是為了什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}活下去的意義...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明已經不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是什麼讓我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快戰鬥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快戰鬥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不會再放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不會再次放棄...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果死了的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就連回想你的事情都辦不到...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論如何我都要贏!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論如何我都要活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底發生了什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人在...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殘殺著...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}拜託了 米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要出事啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎 沒受傷吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們兩個都沒事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之該移動了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不妙 15公尺級的有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不對... 那個巨人他...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給...給他致命一擊了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是了解弱點所在才殺了他的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之我們要移動了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在他過來我們這裡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不對...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他對我們毫無反應...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明直接跑來攻擊我們還比較正常...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我感覺他有著格鬥技的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也只能說他是奇行種吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不清楚的地方還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之我們趕快前往本部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等 米卡莎的瓦斯罐是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}屁啦 真的嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼辦啊 沒有妳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能做的很明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然我的也所剩不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}趕快跟我的交換
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}除此之外別無他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算給我也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次請妳好好珍惜的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是為了拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒有做好「背負著大家的生命」的覺悟就煽動戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在沒有感受到這份責任之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}甚至還曾經放棄過自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且還只是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}機動裝置還可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}刀子也補滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個東西請留下來給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是不想要活著被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...不會吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不會把你丟在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他只是不斷地攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人把巨人殺死這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我聽都沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然而我感到些許興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那片光景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看起來就像是人類憤怒的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殘殺巨人的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因其出現在眼前而動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}瞠目結舌的第104期訓練兵們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}最終 在他們面前現身的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
